{"word":"ἐμπορεύομαι","slug":"ἐμπορεύομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐμπορεύομαι</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>-πορεύσομαι</el>) (aor1 <el>ἐνεπορεύθην</el>) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἐν'><el>ἐν</el></a>\n<p/><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to travel</i>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>to travel for traffic, to be a merchant, to trade, traffic</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> rei, <i>to import</i>, <b><a href='S:Lucian'>Luc.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>3. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> <a href='S:person, personal'>pers.</a> <i>to make gain of, to overreach</i>, <b><a href='S:New Testament'>NTest.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}